title: Hero and the Terror-Chuck Norris

Movie Description
A determined policeman (Chuck Norris) tracks a mad killer down to the Santa Monica pier. When the crook accidentally trips, the cop succeeds in capturing him, and the public heaps praise on the arresting officer. But then the maniac escapes, and the frightened cop has to prove he deserves to be called a hero.

Credits 
Cast: Chuck Norris 
Director: William Tannen 

Synopsis
The hero is an L.A. cop who relives a near-fatal confrontation with a Herculean ex-con while showing his emotional side during his pregnant girlfriend's labor and delivery.
